    "body" : "<p>This should work (untested, based on JavaDoc):</p>\n\n<pre><code>DecimalFormat formatter = (DecimalFormat) NumberFormat.getInstance(Locale.US);\nDecimalFormatSymbols symbols = formatter.getDecimalFormatSymbols();\n\nsymbols.setGroupingSeparator(' ');\nformatter.setDecimalFormatSymbols(symbols);\nSystem.out.println(formatter.format(bd.longValue()));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>According to the JavaDoc, the cast in the first line should be save for most locales.</p>\n"
