    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>try this code to format as used in Brazil:</p>\n\n<pre><code>    DecimalFormat df = new DecimalFormat(\n      \"#,##0.00\", \n      new DecimalFormatSymbols(new Locale(\"pt\", \"BR\")));\n\n    BigDecimal value = new BigDecimal(123456.00);\n\n    System.out.println(df.format(value.floatValue()));\n\n    // results: \"123.456,00\"\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1077468,
      "reputation" : 21675,
      "user_id" : 1075289,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 65,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/dLGwi.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Amio.io",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1075289/amio-io"
