      "comment_id" : 104161734,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "This was an epiphany.  However, you really have to stress, that &quot;,&quot; is only a flag, not the character it uses as a group separator. (Took me some time to find the issue.) See <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/Formatter.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/Formatter.html</a>"
    } ],
