    "question_id" : 5323502,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are using thousand separator for Integer data type use 1.</p>\n<p><strong>1. For integer data Type</strong></p>\n<pre><code>String.format(&quot;%,d\\n&quot;, 58625)\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Output:</strong></p>\n<pre><code>58,625\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>2. For Floating Point data Type</strong></p>\n<pre><code>String.format(&quot;%,.2f&quot;,58625.21)\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Output:</strong></p>\n<pre><code>58,625.21\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
